oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (black on white) announcing the 16th Annual Guitar Pull with Hunter Hayes, Joe Nichols, Kip Moore, Dustin Lynch, Thompson Square and Dan + Shay at the James Brown Arena on November 18. Poster features a woodcut of a guitar. Poster is a separate for a complete poster.
